{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"深宫惊变\"，揭开叶孤城与西门吹雪决战夜的宫廷阴谋。唐天纵以追魂砂击中假叶孤城（实为黑衣人替身），真相败露。陆小凤识破叶孤城以替身应战的诡计，推断出宫中太监王安可能盗出缎带，急欲面见皇帝。魏子云犹豫再三后同意带路，途中遭遇十三名黑衣人伏击，丁敖从暗处出剑斩杀紫衣人首领，黑衣人全灭。与此同时，王安趁皇帝熟睡之际，将与皇帝容貌极为相似的南王世子引至御前，企图李代桃僵篡夺皇位。皇帝虽被困，却暗中召出鱼家四兄弟护卫，叶孤城及时赶到以天外飞仙一剑破七星剑阵。皇帝与叶孤城展开\"王贼之辩\"，叶孤城被皇帝\"心中有剑\"之论所动，犹豫之际陆小凤赶到阻止刺杀。叶孤城逃出南书房，西门吹雪在月下等候，二人论剑道精义——\"诚\"字。魏子云率大军包围，西门吹雪要求与叶孤城公平一战，以生死荣辱为赌。全章在陆小凤从枪林刀山中走出时戛然而止，留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "解药，快拿解药来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_tian_zong",
      "speaker_name": "唐天纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我大哥二哥都伤在你剑下，不死也成残废，你跟我们唐家仇深如海，你还想要我的解药？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那是叶孤城的事，与我完全没有关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_tian_zong",
      "speaker_name": "唐天纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你不是叶孤城？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_tian_zong",
      "speaker_name": "唐天纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？叶孤城呢？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事？简直连我也糊涂了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "糊涂的是你，不是我！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道叶孤城自己为什么不来？你知道他的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道宫里有个姓王的老太监？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王总管？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是他，他能不能将缎带盗出来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "太子还未即位时，他本是在南书房伴读的，大行皇帝去世，太子登基，他就成了当今皇上面前的红人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只问你，除了你们外，他是不是也能将缎带盗出来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在皇上是不是已就寝了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇上励精图治，早朝从不间断，所以每天都睡得很早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "睡在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇上登基虽已很久，却还是和做太子时一样读书不倦，所以还是常歇在南书房。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南书房在哪里呢？快快带我去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我们带你去见皇上？你疯了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有疯，可是你们若不肯带我去，你们就快疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人真的疯了，不但自己胡说八道，还想要我们脑袋搬家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是想要你们脑袋搬家，是想保全你们的脑袋。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姑且再信你这一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的要带他去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们也全都跟着我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你居然敢在这里杀人？你不知道这是砍头的罪名？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "反正头也不是我的，再多砍几个也无妨。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢动一动，这里的人头就又得少一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住口！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已不能动，连骂骂人都不行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是在骂谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听不出我是在骂谁？我再骂给你听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_xian",
      "speaker_name": "殷羡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他管骂人，我管杀人……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚，你知不知道这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事你不该问和尚的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我应该去问谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶孤城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在这里用不着你伺候，退下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还没有走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奴婢还有事上禀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奴婢想请皇上去见一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇上想必不知他是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位就是大行皇帝的嫡裔，南王爷的世子，也就是当今天子的嫡亲堂弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是奉诏入京的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既未奉诏，就擅离封地，该是什么罪名，你知不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇子犯法，与民同罪，朕纵然有心相护，只怕也……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕也免不了是杀头的罪名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然知法，为何还要犯法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知法犯法，罪加一等，朕纵然有心救你一命，怎奈祖宗的家法尚在……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？怎敢对朕如此无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕受命于天，奉诏于先帝，乃是当今天子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王总管。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奴婢在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先把这人押下去，黎明处决。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "念在同是先帝血脉，不妨赐他个全尸，再将他的尸骨兼程送回南王府。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真不懂，放着好好的小王爷不做，却偏偏要上京来送死，这是干什么呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皇子犯法，与民同罪，这道理你既然也知道，你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说，我在听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种荒谬的事，你们是怎么想得出来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来不想说的，可是我实在憋不住了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实告诉你，自从老王爷上次入京，发现你跟小王爷长得几乎一模一样，这件事就已经开始进行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他收买了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不但喜欢赌钱，而且还喜欢嫖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我的开销一向不小，总得找个来路才行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的胆子也不小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的胆子倒不大，不是十拿九稳的事，我是绝不会干的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事已十拿九稳？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们本来还担心魏子云那些兔崽子，可是现在我们已想法子把他们引开了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喜欢下棋的人，假如听见外面有两位大国手在下棋，还能不能呆在屋子里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "学剑的人也一样，若知道当代最负盛名的两位大剑客，就在前面的太和殿上比剑，他们也一样没法子在屋子里呆下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的莫非是西门吹雪和叶孤城？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道？你也知道这两个人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以此两人的剑术和盛名，也就难怪魏子云他们会动心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人心总是肉做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好朕身边还有几个不动心的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "破。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶孤城？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "山野草民，想不到竟能上动天听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天外飞仙，一剑破七星，果然是好剑法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来就是好剑法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卿本佳人，奈何从贼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "成就是王，败就是贼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贼就是贼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以陛下之见识与镇定，武林之中已少有人能及，陛下若入江湖，必可名列十大高手之中。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好眼力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今王已非王，贼已非贼，王贼之间，强者为胜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个强者为胜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的剑已在手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你手中虽有剑，心中却无剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中无剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑直，剑刚，心邪之人，胸中焉能藏剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此时此刻，我手中剑已经够了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手中的剑能伤人，心中的剑却只能伤得自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拔你的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我手中无剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不敢应战？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我练的是天子之剑，平天下，安万民，运筹于帷幄之中，决胜于千里之外，以身当剑，血溅五步是为天子所不取。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕的意思，你想必也已明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你宁愿束手待毙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕受命于天，你敢妄动？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_an",
      "speaker_name": "王安",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，你不杀他，他就要杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "南王世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一定会动手的，名扬天下的'白云城主'，不会有妇人之仁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本不杀手无寸铁之人，今日却要破例一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_di",
      "speaker_name": "皇帝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你手中虽无剑，心中却有剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也说过，手中的剑能伤人，心中的剑却必伤自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么会来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我何必来，你又何必来？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不该来，我不必来，只可惜我们现在都已来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "实在可惜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你学剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道剑的精义何在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在于诚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诚？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "惟有诚心真意，才能达到剑术的巅峰，不诚的人，根本不足论剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不诚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你学剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "学无止境，剑术更是学无止境。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既学剑，就该知道学剑的人只要诚于剑，并不必诚于人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白云城主？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "城主远在天外，剑如飞仙，人也如飞仙，何苦自贬于红尘，作此不智事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不懂？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事，你本就不会懂的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许我不懂，可是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我们却懂得，像你犯这种罪是千刀万段，株连九族的死罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道你犯的是什么罪？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你练刀不成，学剑又不精，敢对我无礼，你犯的也是死罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等一等！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先听我说一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若与叶孤城双剑联手，普天之下，有谁能抵挡？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的意思，你是不是已明白？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我七岁学剑，七年有成，至今未遇敌手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只恐琼楼玉字，高处不胜寒……人在高处的寂寞，他们这些人又怎么会知道呢？你又何必对他们说？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今夜是月圆之夕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是叶孤城？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你掌中有剑，我也有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "叶孤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以，我总算已经有了对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你不愿让他伏法而死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你连王法都不管了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻，我但求与叶城主一战而已，生死荣辱，我都已不放在心上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在你眼中看来，这一战不但重于王法，也重于性命？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "生有何欢，死有何惧，得一知己，死而无憾，能得到白云城主这样的对手，死更无憾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "生死虽轻若鸿毛，王法却重于泰山，我虽然明白你的意思，怎奈……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你逼着我陪他先闯出去，再易地而战么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一战势在必行，你最好赶快拿定主意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    }
